  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-1219add9-7fff-9b65-8347-032ca3d33f8f&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed outbuilding, by reason of its massing, design and location, comprises an over development of the site which results in an unneighbourly form of development, which would be detrimental to the outlook and living conditions of 6 Shrubland Road. As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D3 (Optimising Site Capacity through the Design-led Approach) D6 (Housing Quality and Standards) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020) and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-00080f0c-7fff-4db8-a64d-2d7abb99a654&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The proposed outbuilding, by reason of its scale, massing and siting is considered to result in an overly dominant and incongruous addition that would harm the character and appearance of the subject property and the Graham Road and Mapledene Conservation Area. As such, the proposed development is contrary to policies D1 (Londonâ€™s form, character and capacity for growth), D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and HC1 (Heritage conservation and growth) of the London Plan (2021), policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020) and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009) and the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Graham Road and Mapledene&amp;nbsp; Conservation Area Appraisal (1997). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
